headline.main: How Liberian Women Delivered Africa’s First Female President
headline.print_headline: How Women Delivered Africa’s First Female President

lead_paragraph: The story of how Liberian women upended centuries of male rule in 2005 has acquired a keen relevance as American women who supported Hillary Clinton grapple with the whys of November’s election.
